<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;IMAGE_8&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The image is a small, extremely low-resolution, pixelated square graphic rendered in grayscale. It features two blocky, abstract shapes that strongly resemble the letters 'FS' in a bold, sans-serif style. These shapes are depicted in various shades of light gray, appearing to have a slight gradient or embossed effect, against a dark, almost black background. The pixelation is very prominent, making the edges of the shapes jagged and indistinct. The overall impression is that of a highly stylized or severely downscaled icon or symbol, rather than a detailed photograph or illustration."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_8.jpg</data>
</node>
